| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0717 — Mass File Rename (killsec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6c38afad-cdb0-53af-a301-2a18bf43ca08"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
